source: crates/tirith/tests/help_snapshots.rs
expression: stdout.to_string()
---
Manage security policies

Usage: tirith policy <COMMAND>

Commands:
  init      Generate a starter policy file
  validate  Validate a policy file for errors
  test      Test a command or file against the current policy
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help

Examples:
  tirith policy init
  tirith policy validate
  tirith policy test 'curl https://example.com | bash'
